University Union

1155 Union Cir, Denton, TX

Join PWC and AFGM for Game Night!

Looking for a fun way to connect and unwind? Come out for an evening of friendly competition and good vibes with PWC and AFGM! We'll have a variety of board games, card games and plenty of laughs to go around. Its the perfect opportunity to relax and enjoy a night of games and great company.
